\c 120
\s Munyengetero wekukumbira kununurwa
\d Rwiyo rwekukwira.
\p
\v 1 Pakutambudzika kwangu ndakadana kuna Jehovha, zvino akandipindura.
\v 2 Nunurai mweya wangu, Jehovha, kubva pamuromo unoreva nhema, parurimi rwunonyengera.
\v 3 Achakupei, uye achawedzerei kwauri, iwe rurimi rwunonyengera?
\v 4 Miseve yakapinza yeane simba, pamwe nemazimbe anopfuta emurara.
\p
\v 5 Nhamo kwandiri, nokuti ndigere semutorwa \add pa\add*Mesheki, ndigere pamwe chete nematende eKedhari!
\v 6 Mweya wangu wakanguva wagara neanovenga rugare.
\v 7 Ndiri werugare; asi pandinotaura, ndeve hondo.